data.name: simBrowseButton.ToolTip
data.value:
Press this button to browse for the ORSIM executable Simulation File format should be (.exe)
Note: To save time, name the simulation as ORSIM.exe and save it on the desktop. This way, the simulation will be selected directly when this program is started.
